{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"","page-layout":"custom"},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     HERO\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"hero-content\">\n    <div class=\"badge-eafit\">Centro de Valor PГәblico вҖ” Universidad EAFIT</div>\n    <h1>InvestigaciГіn aplicada<br>para el sector pГәblico</h1>\n    <p class=\"subtitle\">\n      Generamos conocimiento riguroso y acompaГұamos procesos de transformaciГіn\n      institucional en Colombia. Nuestros proyectos combinan evidencia acadГ©mica\n      con impacto en polГӯtica pГәblica.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     PROYECTOS\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"section-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"section-title\">\n    <h2>Proyectos</h2>\n    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"projects-grid\">\n\n    <!-- Proyecto Provincias -->\n    <a class=\"project-card\" href=\"https://cvp-eafit.github.io/provincias\" target=\"_blank\">\n      <div class=\"card-accent\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(90deg, #003DA5, #00A859);\"></div>\n      <div class=\"card-body\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag text-cvp-blue\">Gobierno Territorial В· Antioquia</div>\n        <h3>Fortalecimiento de Esquemas Asociativos Territoriales</h3>\n        <p>\n          ConsultorГӯa con la GobernaciГіn de Antioquia para fortalecer las\n          Provincias Administrativas y de PlanificaciГіn (PAP): planes estratГ©gicos,\n          delegaciГіn de competencias y sistematizaciГіn de la experiencia asociativa.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"card-footer-meta\">\n          <span>2025вҖ“2026 В· DAP Antioquia</span>\n          <span class=\"card-status status-active\">в—Ҹ Activo</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </a>\n\n    <!-- Placeholder 2 -->\n    <div class=\"project-card\" style=\"opacity: 0.6; cursor: default;\">\n      <div class=\"card-accent\" style=\"background: #e0e0e0;\"></div>\n      <div class=\"card-body\">\n        <div class=\"card-tag\" style=\"color: #aaa;\">PrГіximamente</div>\n        <h3 style=\"color: #aaa;\">Nuevo proyecto</h3>\n        <p style=\"color: #bbb;\">\n          PrГіximamente publicaremos los resultados de nuevas investigaciones\n          y consultorГӯas del Centro de Valor PГәblico.\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"card-footer-meta\">\n          <span style=\"color: #ccc;\">вҖ”</span>\n          <span class=\"card-status status-coming\">PrГіximo</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     SOBRE EL CVP\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"about-section\">\n  <div class=\"section-title\">\n    <h2>Sobre el Centro</h2>\n    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"about-content\">\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar-icon\" style=\"background: #e8eef8;\">рҹ”¬</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar-text\">\n        <h4>InvestigaciГіn rigurosa</h4>\n        <p>Combinamos mГ©todos cuantitativos y cualitativos para generar evidencia\n        sГіlida sobre polГӯticas pГәblicas y gestiГіn territorial.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar-icon\" style=\"background: #e8f8f0;\">рҹӨқ</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar-text\">\n        <h4>Alianzas estratГ©gicas</h4>\n        <p>Trabajamos con entidades del gobierno, organismos internacionales\n        y organizaciones de la sociedad civil.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar-icon\" style=\"background: #e8eef8;\">рҹ“Ҡ</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar-text\">\n        <h4>Ciencia abierta</h4>\n        <p>Nuestros datos, cГіdigo y metodologГӯas son pГәblicos y reproducibles,\n        siguiendo los principios de ciencia abierta.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"pillar\">\n      <div class=\"pillar-icon\" style=\"background: #e8f8f0;\">рҹҺҜ</div>\n      <div class=\"pillar-text\">\n        <h4>Impacto en polГӯtica pГәblica</h4>\n        <p>Traducimos la investigaciГіn en recomendaciones accionables para\n        tomadores de decisiones en el sector pГәblico colombiano.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     ALIADOS\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"partners-section\">\n  <div class=\"section-title\">\n    <h2>Aliados institucionales</h2>\n    <div class=\"divider\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"partners-logos\">\n    <div class=\"partner-badge\">GobernaciГіn de Antioquia</div>\n    <div class=\"partner-badge\">DAP Antioquia</div>\n    <div class=\"partner-badge\">Universidad EAFIT</div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<!-- в•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\n     HERO\nв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ -->\n<div class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"hero-content\">\n    <div class=\"badge-eafit\">Centro de Valor PГәblico вҖ” Universidad EAFIT</div>\n    <h1>InvestigaciГіn aplicada<br>para el sector pГәblico</h1>\